These products allow you to develop as a console application, and GUI applications, including technology to support Windows Forms, and Web sites,

.NET Framework, Xbox, Windows Phone .NET Compact Framework and Silverlight.
Create cross-platform applications for Windows, iOS, Android and other platforms using a single integrated development environment.

Additional Information:

The procedure for treatment:
1. Run the studio;
2. Open the "Help" menu;
3. Select the item "Register a product";
4. Click on the label "Enter Key" (located at the bottom right);
5. Insert the key into the field and click "Apply".
